<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>blog web</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs")%>
    
        <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom" style="font-size: 50px;">BLOGGING WEB</h2>
    
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 align-items-md-center g-5 py-5">
          <div class="col d-flex flex-column align-items-start gap-2">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-body-emphasis">BLOGGING</h2>
            <p class="text-body-secondary" style="text-align: justify;">Blogging has become an indispensable tool for individuals and businesses alike, offering a dynamic platform for sharing insights, promoting products, and engaging with a global audience. Whether you're a seasoned writer or a novice, the world of blogging opens doors to endless possibilities. It allows you to express your unique voice, build a community of like-minded readers, and establish yourself as an authority in your niche. In today's digital age, where content is king, a well-crafted blog not only boosts your online presence but also drives traffic, fosters trust, and creates opportunities for monetization. Embrace the power of blogging and transform your passion into a thriving digital venture.</p>
           
          </div>
    
          <div class="col">
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 g-4">
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">CREATE BLOG</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Here by clicking below button you can create a blog</p>
                <a href="/create"><button class="btn btn-secondary rounded-pill px-3" type="button">Create</button></a>
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">VIEW BLOG</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Here by clicking below button you can view your blog</p>
               <a href="/view"><button class="btn btn-secondary rounded-pill px-3" type="button">View</button></a> 
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">UPDATE BLOG</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Here by clicking below button you can update a blog</p>
                <a href="/update"><button class="btn btn-secondary rounded-pill px-3" type="button">Update</button></a>
              </div>
    
              <div class="col d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="feature-icon-small d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-4 rounded-3">
                  
                </div>
                <h4 class="fw-semibold mb-0 text-body-emphasis">DELETE BLOG</h4>
                <p class="text-body-secondary">Here by clicking below button you can delete a blog</p>
                <a href="/delete"><button class="btn btn-secondary rounded-pill px-3" type="button">Delete</button></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%- include("partials/footer.ejs")%>
      

      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>